    Summary:
      check for TranslationService before installing Localizer's
    Revision:
      Localizer--main--1.1--patch-33

    Check wether the product "TranslationService" is installed before
    deploying the Localizer's translation service. This is a backwards
    compatibility fix to avoid breaking existing sites that use the
    "TranslationService" product.
    
